      <title>Shinobi no Satori</title>
      <author>Catzy123</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/641335</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/641335#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">3e6b8f5e5b84d3c2124a40f59a6d7739483430c7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 03:07:57 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694a82c1cec3e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd38eb2e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd3b9624.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd365a23.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd367669.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd364f84.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd36b2a1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd39f91f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd36677c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd361a8d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd36f0b0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd384776.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd3a1980.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd39fd6f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd3a25d4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694aabd39f89a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694ac25134432.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694ac6cab1f05.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/694ac74da6ff8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/699b5abfbd326.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Bomb fix&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read Below for the real Update i added&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: The "Explosions" option wasnt working in TKMM, now does again.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shinobi Mod that turns Link into a Real Shinobi, took a ton of time and effort and learning and creativity to make this but now its complete.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Once you wear a specific armor piece- Link gains abilities, i will List what each armor piece gives for a ability&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;                                      &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;        UPDATE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Sword Equip and Unequip has Improved Visuals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/equip.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Now works on Version &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.0 - 1.4.3&lt;/span&gt; With Tkmm and also without Tkmm and Switch (tested)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Talisman effect is now&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; standalone&lt;/span&gt;, so the yiga will keep their Red Talisman always&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The World &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;doesnt pause&lt;/span&gt; anymore when De/Activating the Master Sword&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Speed Wind effect&lt;/span&gt; lines to all the Shinobi actions (like running and double jumping, more visible while in shadows)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed all Bugs like the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;T-posing during backflip&lt;/span&gt; and the Raurus arm glow after every cutscene&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Landing in Water also &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;resets&lt;/span&gt; double jumps now&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No Double Jumps in &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Shrines&lt;/span&gt; anymore -_-&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shinobi Mask-&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/tp.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;A headband that gives temporary Sheikah knowledge.&lt;br&gt;it grants the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;ability to double jump, air dodge with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;L&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;, or leap forward with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;A&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;, the hood can be lowered by double-tapping&lt;/span&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;A&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;while standing still and holding&lt;/span&gt; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;B&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; (The Hylian Hood can also be lowered this way).&lt;br&gt;It &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Enables&lt;/span&gt; Master Sword Beams without full health too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/tp2.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;It also gives Link a whole Sheikah movement overhaul like with my other mod &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/450989"&gt;Sheikah Techniques&lt;/a&gt; but its not as much.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shinobi Chest Guard-&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/ms_e91a9.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;An ancient chest piece made of Sheikah wisdom and &lt;br&gt;Zonai power, its fabric is torn and worn, yet it lets the&lt;br&gt;wearer &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;unleash the Master Sword's true power by&lt;br&gt;holding&lt;/span&gt; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;ZL&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;while standing still and double-tapping&lt;/span&gt; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;A&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;It has Master Sword beam dmg &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;up&lt;/span&gt; too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Zonai and Sheikah arm are also both &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Reactive&lt;/span&gt; to the new abilities.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;(The sword goes into the Ultimate form, 60 Dmg and Unbreakable).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shinobi Tight's-&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/wr_a676c.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sheikah wisdom is mixed with Zonai power in these &lt;br&gt;tights, enabling the wearer to sprint swiftly&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;across the surface of water.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;It &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;prevents&lt;/span&gt; fall dmg too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;How do you get the armor?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;Once you get the PurahPad inside your inventory, you will automatically get a quest when you are in game, follow the quest and you will obtain it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;And once you beat the quest you will get a Talisman that will give the same abilities also to some Vanilla Armor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;And if you sell the armor then you can buy it again in &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;CeCe’s&lt;/span&gt; shop.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;How Compatible is the mod?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod is mostly standalone and works with everything if placed at the top of TKMM. &lt;b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="87"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;However&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, because it uses a custom ASB file to control its unique animations, it will clash with big mods like Challenge Mode or DAR. Since ASB files are a nightmare to merge manually, those mods will likely lose some of their animation or attack edits if used together. Same with Ainb- but that file controls more like abilities like other Armor ability mods&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For Sheikah Techniques, you shouldn't play them together, it will feel messy, i recommend to chose only one or the other here.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1 class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Mod Supports both &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;English and German&lt;/span&gt;, and for Game versions its only &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.0 - 1.4.3&lt;/span&gt; Both with and without Tkmm and on Switch (Tested)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Install Insturctions&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Emulator&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip file and then right click totk and place the mod in Mod Data Location&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Switch&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip and search the "romfs" folder and place it in "atmosphere\content\0100F2C0115B6000" on your sdcard&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;To merge with other mods&lt;/span&gt;, download the mod merger: &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftotkmods.github.io%2Ftkmm%2Fdownloads%2F&amp;follow=true" target="_blank"&gt;TKMM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Theres also options for different talisman color or disable the Glow/God-Voices/Cape, but for that you will need to install the .tkcl with &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tools/17165"&gt;TKMM&lt;/a&gt;. And the talisman color change also affects yiga's for now.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Watch the whole Video if you want to see everything that the Armor does but there's two small things i didn't say and that's that Link is also able to Jump cancel out of Sword Flurry Rushes and that 2 Handed Swords are faster.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;My &lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/catzy123" target="_blank"&gt;Ko-fi&lt;/a&gt;, if you want to support me making more mods like these &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Have fun with the mod!</description>
