      <guid isPermaLink="false">830f2c1af9f1f42ded322d478fe8f1282f375c47</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 00:10:45 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67745e34d9fb0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e2338f909.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e233cb3e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67a2f9ce58590.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2736150.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d295a71d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556aa1d3c4f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67a2f9cec1c31.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2886007.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68241f9ae12d1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68241f6224f43.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68241fa8e6838.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6824243f45ef5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d29e262e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2a13128.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/656e429b3151f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f512adc45.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d275ec12.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65539491ce10f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6588ebe49c0f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59c82d44.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59d01b67.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a262b3208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a5730e99c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a0543b9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; 1.4.0+ Feature Parity + TKCL Update&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This update coincides with the release of &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://tkmm.org/"&gt;TKMM v2.1.1&lt;/a&gt;, which fixes multiple issues for users on game versions 1.4.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is recommended to uninstall any previous versions of The Second Quest from TKMM before downloading the latest version of the mod.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Amendment&lt;/em&gt;: Updated the "Mineru Weapon Durability Cap Removal" patch to function on game versions 1.4.0+&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Amendment&lt;/em&gt;: Updated the audio quality-of-life changes to function on game versions 1.4.0+&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: "Disable Warp Cost" option added to the TKCL.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: "Low Hearts Sound" option added to the TKCL.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;Rediscover Hyrule Kingdom&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Tears of the Kingdom: The Second Quest &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;is a large-scale mod being co-developed by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2343073"&gt;deadpanned&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2792161"&gt;YourDiamondDog&lt;/a&gt;,&#13;
 which remixes, rebalances, and reimagines many elements of Tears of the&#13;
 Kingdom to deliver an exciting New Game experience for veteran players &#13;
or first-time players who favor a modded take on &lt;i&gt;The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom&lt;/i&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;It is strongly recommended to start a new save file for the best experience!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Switch users: Please read the section under compatibility info pertaining to the "exefs" folder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Overhauled Combat Mechanics&lt;/span&gt; faithful to the game's core vision of a versatile physics-based combat system.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Rebalanced Weapons and Materials&lt;/span&gt; to emphasize real-time tactics and more diverse fusion combinations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Diversified Enemies&lt;/span&gt; boasting new properties, greater intelligence, and stronger equipment all across Hyrule.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Reworked World Scaling and Economy&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;All-New Yiga Schematics and Schema Stones&lt;/span&gt; courtesy of &lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/HyruleEngineering/" target="_blank"&gt;The Hyrule Engineering Club&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Remixed Loot, Armor, and Legendary Weapon&lt;/span&gt; locations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;New Armor and Legendary Weapons&lt;/span&gt; to discover.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Overhauled Quest Rewards&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;More Challenging Weather Conditions&lt;/span&gt; across Hyrule, the Skies, and the Depths, including new underground biomes and color palettes to increase visual diversity.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Overhauled Health Restoration System&lt;/span&gt;, further improved from &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472675"&gt;Cook or Die&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Overhauled Armor System&lt;/span&gt;, further improved from&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472574"&gt; Total Armor Rebalance&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Additional Armor Sets Improvable&lt;/span&gt; to raise defense or grant set bonuses.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Updated Text &lt;/span&gt;including new loading screen tips, tutorial text, and NPC &#13;
dialogue that matches changes to the mechanics and world.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Quality of Life Elements and Unofficial Bug Fixes&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;For a comprehensive list of changes and additions, see: &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1COwsDfkoxHEwlsqFNRuSNPhQXo73VKI_nAasYEbfoII"&gt;The Second Quest Spreadsheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1COwsDfkoxHEwlsqFNRuSNPhQXo73VKI_nAasYEbfoII"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Planned Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Localization for all supported languages.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shrine entrances remixed to lead to different shrines.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Schematics optimized for 60 FPS compatibility.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mod Customization Options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;...And More!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Compatibility Info:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Compatible game versions:&lt;b&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.4.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.4.1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.4.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.4.3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Installation for Switch Users:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor SelectedElement"&gt;Please note: For game versions 1.4.0+ (Switch Firmware 20+) the romfslite feature from &lt;a href="https://github.com/MaxLastBreath/nx-optimizer" target="_blank"&gt;NX Optimizer&lt;/a&gt; (included in &lt;a href="https://tkmm.org/" target="_blank"&gt;TKMM&lt;/a&gt; by default) is required to load large mods.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Copy The Second Quest's &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;romfs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; folder (rename to &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;romfslite&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; on versions 1.4.0+) and &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;exefs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; folder into &lt;b&gt;atmosphere/contents/"TitleID"&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Navigate to &lt;b&gt;atmosphere/contents/"TitleID"/exefs&lt;/b&gt;. Locate the &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;IPS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; file inside and cut + paste it inside &lt;b&gt;atmosphere/exefs_patches/TSQ&lt;/b&gt; (create a new folder named TSQ if one does not exist).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have multiple mods that edit these files, use &lt;a href="https://tkmm.org/docs/" target="_blank"&gt;TKMM (Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager)&lt;/a&gt; to merge them:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ResourceSizeTable.Product.&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;RSDB&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Mals&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tag.Product&lt;/span&gt;.{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;GameDataList.Product.110.byml&lt;/span&gt; file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Banc&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Event&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the {&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Actor&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;.pack&lt;/span&gt; files for armor, weapons, food, enemies, Zonai devices, and the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Player.pack&lt;/span&gt; file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Featured Engineers: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCThhMsHtYHWvd_jri49FInQ" target="_blank"&gt;2CPhoenix&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;BlazingAlchemist991&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@chesepuf" target="_blank"&gt;chesepuf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;Efficienct_Demand5759&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;FantasticPound&lt;br&gt;GoNinjaPro&lt;br&gt;LongJumpingFrame&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ofstrings2/" target="_blank"&gt;OfStrings2&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ofstrings2" target="_blank"&gt;Wood, Rubber, &amp; Glue&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://on.soundcloud.com/ixGuV" target="_blank"&gt;OshKoshGanache&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Scared_Cry_4931/" target="_blank"&gt;SacredCry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Shak404/" target="_blank"&gt;Shak404&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shlowpoke&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtube.com/@ytshotmaker" target="_blank"&gt;Shotmaker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/susannediazz/" target="_blank"&gt;Suusi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/Swapdoodle" target="_blank"&gt;Swapdoodle&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Virama&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Ultrababouin/" target="_blank"&gt;Ultrababouin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Zhujzal</description>
