      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eee27cd612.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf53dc4e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf5ba713.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf5d07f4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf5db307.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf655d40.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf6d4a20.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf689143.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3eedf6c1946.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hey!&amp;nbsp;It’s been quite a long time, hasn’t it? This time I bring to the game an armor set based on High Lord Wolnir, from Dark Souls III, and his weapon:&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Wolnir's Holy Sword&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I also want to say that I'll soon be releasing a mod for another game, one I've never modded before.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-The armor gives you the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Stealth Up&lt;/span&gt; effect when equiped. When equiped the whole set, you earn the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Attack Up with bone weapons&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Stal &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Disguise&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;effects; it also will &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Frighten People&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(the last 3 only when equiped the whole set with the skull as helmet, not as hood).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;All pieces have &lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;16&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;defense each one, and can´t be upgraded.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;-The&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Wolnir's Holy Sword&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;makes &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;60 of damage&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The sword&amp;nbsp;has a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;light effect&lt;/span&gt;, and shoots &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Darknes Arrows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;IT´S A BONE WEAPON&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The helmet´s jaw moves along with Link’s jaw.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The armor and weapon can be purchased from Beedle at &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Outskirt Stable&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only tested on &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;1.2.1&lt;/span&gt;, and the armor and weapon names are for the US english.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To support me, you can commission mods through Discord (There are certain issues with Checkpoint), or donate something via &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fsombra395&amp;amp;follow=true"&gt;Ko-fi&lt;/a&gt;</description>
