    <item>
      <title>Link of the Silent Sorrow.</title>
      <author>Porroman420</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/672037</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/672037#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">4010ce931fbfaf2b086c1b9da18886f02828d0ae</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 09:02:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69eba5b91e620.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3b94cea7e0a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3b9d895bccc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69ebae647b4bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69ebaa5ea0c4d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69eba5f681f23.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69fee6a2d95b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a0990a1e031c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a09912d391be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a099168d6794.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69fee2d02c316.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69fee318c5e24.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; New Quest - Summa Blasphemia&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello, and i hope you had fun with Mea Culpa :D, i changed how you get the items :&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You must agree to a quest you can trigger by removing the sword stuck into the chest of the lady statue outside of the room of awakening, this is the only way to get the items now(if you haven't before), as it's part of the "vibe" the original game has, with how cruel the Miracle is and so on i guess.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It's a new final mission that involves the final boss (Ganondorf), be wary ... as the miracle always watches and will impose it's will if you DO agree to complete it, a little scary surprise for people who decide to try to complete the quest with more of "what" the statue ask, and a "divine punishment" for those who decide to break the weapon condition from the quest.... or force more of "that" special requirement (AKA cheats will not work :P ) :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;NOT COMPATIBLE WITH MODS THAT EDIT THESE EVENTS !!! - MUST BE PLACED ABOVE OF SUCH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Dm_ED_0002.bfevfl.zs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Dm_GA_0022.bfevfl.zs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Those who take uppon the challenge and complete it, post a screenshot on the comment section and be part of the Brotherhood of the Silent Sorrow :D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;If you do get one of the  "divine punishments" casted uppon you share your experience ! :D just for the fun haha&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;weapon damage was increased from 30 to 60 dmg to compensate ... i think.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ROMFS VERSION will be uploaded a bit later ... since internet is messy, as always so you can see how it was made and re-use anything useful.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added new quest into the game, can be started at any point (even on 100% saves)&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Changed how you get the items&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hello friends, as always i hope ya´ll are having lots of fun ! today i wanna share with you also another thing i i wanted to make for quite a time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;THIS MOD EDITS elink2.Product.110.belnk.zs FILE, MUST BE ON TOP OF OTHER WEAPONS THAT EDIT THIS FILE  (COMPATIBILITY PATCH INSIDE ROOT), ALSO COMPATIBLE WITH MY OTHER MODS : Link - Warrior of Sunlight and Master Deity Sword&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;TKMM RECOMMENDED ORDER :&lt;br&gt;- Master Deity Sword&lt;br&gt;- Link - Warrior of Sunlight&lt;br&gt;- Link of the Silent Sorrow&lt;br&gt;- below you can put any other mod that edits the mentioned file above :D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Armorset of The Penitent One and Mea Culpa sword from BLASPHEMOUS.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Merciful be the heart!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Penitent One armorset found at the Room of Awakening let's you depart on pilgrimage since the start of the game to free Hyrule from evil forces across any climate, or terrain but be wary, as part of your penitence is to be humble as your armor offers the most basic physical protection, and doesn't make you unfreezable, unburnable or shockproof &lt;span class="SelectedElement"&gt;and yet that divine will, equally pious and cruel on it's twisted will has granted 3x attack up to each armorpiece, and full miasma protection, as Link is also a chosen one among The Mysteries of the Miracle and it´s convoluted reasons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Graceful be the heart Hylia's chosen one, as Mea Culpa was left behind by something or someone at your disposal, it yearns to torn appart the curse of this land with it's thorns and just like the warrior before you, grasp it tightly, and when you feel how the figure of the Twisted One fuses and pierces your flesh, you will be able to throw with full healt Fervorous Blood using the R button ... this mysterious energy resembles miasma ... but it's your gloomed blood purified and blessed by the sword, effective against evil !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Head piece : some electric resistance, lv2 heat resistance (without shockproof)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Upper piece : Lv2 fire resistance (doesn't make you fireproof)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Leg piece : Lv2 cold resistance (doesn't make you unfreezable)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;you can walk on sand and snow, also you will not slip while climbing, with all three pieces you will get the 4 miasma hearts&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All armorpieces have 3 defense only, 9 in total with all three, but have great attackup values&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Sword does the same as the vanilla master sword 100%, with the buff and all but with guardenhance,rush damage up, and 2x times fuse, 100% unbreakable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;New update adds a true blood slash builded uppon the sidon water shootable for the long sword with R button that is extra effective against miasma. it does 30 dmg and can hurt ANY kind of enemy :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;have fun !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/link_of_the_silent_sorrow_472af.zip" type="application/zip"/>
