Big shout out to &lt;a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1590103"&gt;Fooni&lt;/a&gt;, creator of the &lt;a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/167785"&gt;Keyblade Mods Collection&lt;/a&gt; for BOTW. I used the models from that mod. Not every Keyblade is included here, since TOTK has fewer swords than BOTW.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
