      <title>Link - Warrior of Sunlight</title>
      <author>Porroman420</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/668886</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/668886#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">8abd07da7df4b71b990d3185b8f9dfabbcc994e7</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 11:33:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69db7e2678ee2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a2be938de578.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69db7fccee2c5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a099519bf2cf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a09962b41164.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69df67ef7521a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69df6b639c455.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69df681e5a6e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69df68402c06a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69db7f44cedd2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69db7f82ee01d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Sunlight Altar quest&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello and as always i hope you are having fun, i thought i was not gonna do a new update but here we are :&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I changed how you can get the weapons, now you have to finish a small quest for the Sunlight Altar, wchich uppon completion it's gonna reward you with the weapons&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;you can complete the quest if you have 3 pieces of the three types of gleeok horns, but the fuse will only be available for "covenant members" (players who got the armor and didn't rushed to finish the quest if having the horns already by talking with it again.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;each time you speak with it it's gonna gift you 5 fuses(only if you got the armor) and restore any of the sunlight weapons you lost (only after completing the quest)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sunlight altar is now a fully working standalone bargainer statue with custom dialogue, it can reveal other bargainer statue locations + is gonna have the same unlockable inventory as the one at lookout landing, you can interact and trigger the quest as soon you start the game, it's not gonna affect the lookout landing vanilla statue as this is a stuatue of light, and those are kinda cursed LOL, will reveal the location of "the giants of the depths" for 10 poes always instead of a hundred after the first time.... to make worth visiting it multiple times :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;GET THE ARMOR as the sunlight altar will know...it's watching you :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;have fun!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Changed how you acquire the weapons, now locked behind a quest.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: Now you can get the weapons for free, but first, the quest :V (the final reward only after you completed quest + have the armor on pouch)&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hello, and as always i hope you are having fun ! today i wanna share guys something i was just messing with :D &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;THIS MOD EDITS elink2.Product.110.belnk.zs FILE, MUST BE ON TOP OF OTHER WEAPONS THAT EDIT THIS FILE  (COMPATIBILITY PATCH INSIDE ROOT), ALSO COMPATIBLE WITH MY OTHER MODS : Link - Warrior of Sunlight and Master Deity Sword&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;TKMM RECOMMENDED ORDER :&lt;br&gt;- Elink2 compatibility patch (on top or first places of TKMM)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Master Deity Sword&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Link - Warrior of Sunlight&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Link of the Silent Sorrow&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;- below you can put any other mod that edits the mentioned file above :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Pray at the Sunlight Altar, defeat the mightiest dragons ! and become a Warrior of Sunlight !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The armor pieces are located in the king gleeok sky islands ! defeat all of them, claim their horns and prove your worth at the altar !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Once you complete the quest, the Sunlight Altar is gonna give you the weapons, to get the sunlight blade getting the armor is a must !&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- New Item added - The Sunlight Blade miracle ! does 60 dmg when fused and has fire\electric attacks, invisible fuse, doesn't hide the blade and grants flames on swing !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Sunlight Talisman has a glowy particle effect, does 5 physical + electric damage and can cast the mighty Sunlight Spears at full power that do 60 dmg, veryeffective against evil !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Sunlight Straight Sword has the Master Sword buff and can also shoot a less powerful version of the sunlight spear with R button, has 2x times fuse, with the power of the sun cleanse evil forces from hyrule!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="SelectedElement"&gt;- Sunlight Shield is frictionless and 100% unbreakable !  , and shockproof&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Iron helm grants 100% electric elemental protection &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Armor of the sun grants 100% heat/fire resistance&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Iron leggings grants 100% cold /freeze resistance, + some bonus effects (some are secret jeje)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- All armorpieces grant their respective elemental combat bonuses :D, all together grant the 4 miasma guard hearts &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Sunlight Altar can be found at the highest spot at the Great Sky Island (above the Room of Awakening)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In case you lost, or decide to display the weapons at Link´s house they acquired again :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;if you encounter any issue let me know :D</description>
