      <guid isPermaLink="false">ca8aa64c00f6f505523af3d632a05c4294186ed6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 15:35:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e2a252.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e3c961.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e4b883.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e1e0d7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e0abe5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e21868.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e2a360.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e2e163.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e3f037.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e43fa4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e50f94.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5fd6e5ea8f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69f5ffcd24651.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a0a5055a8a3d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Update&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Feature&lt;/em&gt;: Stellan Gio's Saber has folding animation on the guard.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Amendment&lt;/em&gt;: Changed Luke Skywalker's blade colour to Green.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: Reduced friction of Jedi/Sith shields when surfing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Added missing items from shop &amp; removed duplicates.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;This was requested months ago and I have only just got around to finishing it and I thought that I would post it here too (Just in time for Star Wars Day!!!).&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;A strange visitor to the land has these items for purchase at Riverside Stable Well for 500 Rupees each!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is this?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a collection of &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;50&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;* Lightsabers and 2 Shields.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Saber features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Since Sabers can burn, they all do &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;fire damage&lt;/span&gt; unless stated otherwise.&lt;br&gt;All Sabers do&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; 30 base damage&lt;/span&gt; (This is increased when awakened/near gloom enemies/bosses - Does not show in menu).&lt;br&gt;All weapons have &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;350 durability&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Animated blades&lt;/span&gt; when sheathing/unsheathing the weapon.&lt;br&gt;All &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;custom short range projectiles&lt;/span&gt; (On RB/Throw) do ~24 Damage &amp; also causes knockback to enemies (Also doubles damage when near gloom enemies/bosses EXCEPT for Electric Projectiles).&lt;br&gt;Jedi Sabers have an aura when "Awakened" (Others do not).&lt;br&gt;Phantom fuses (Blade does not hide when fused).&lt;br&gt;Has &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;custom Saber sounds&lt;/span&gt;/SLink2 for sheathing/unsheathing/attacking.&lt;br&gt;All Sabers are able to be added to compendium.&lt;br&gt;Shields have 150 Defence and 200 Durability.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Specific weapon details:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Luke Skywalker&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Yoda&lt;/b&gt; - Electric damage and Electric-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kylo Ren&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Maul&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Obi-Wan Kenobi&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Malgus&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Harlon&lt;/b&gt; - Water Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Count Dooku&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Qui-Gon Jinn&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Inquisitor&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darksaber&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rey Skywalker&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mace Windu&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cal Kestis&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ancient Sith&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Gungi&lt;/b&gt; - Electric damage and Electric-Satori Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ahsoka Tano&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Vader &lt;/b&gt;- Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Exar Kun&lt;/b&gt; - Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Temple Guard&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ronin&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rahm Kota&lt;/b&gt; - Electric-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Orgus Din&lt;/b&gt; - Electric-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kyle Katarn&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Sidious&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Arcann&lt;/b&gt; - Electric Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Revan&lt;/b&gt; (Purple) - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Darth Revan&lt;/b&gt; (Red) - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ezra Bridger&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lord Starkiller&lt;/b&gt; - Fire Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;*Added in v1.0.2:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Anakin Skywalker&lt;/b&gt; - Electric-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stellan Gios&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Din Grogu&lt;/b&gt; - Electric-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Plo Koon&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ancient Jedi Saber&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Royal Elegance&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Uneti Root &lt;/b&gt;- Electric projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kanan Jarrus&lt;/b&gt; - Electric-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Qu-Rahn&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;High Republic Jedi &lt;/b&gt;- Ice-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Droid Lightsaber&lt;/b&gt; - Elec-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lana Beniko&lt;/b&gt; - Fireball Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tavion Axmis &lt;/b&gt;- Fireball Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Wampa Tooth&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Desann&lt;/b&gt; - Gloom Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Medieval&lt;/b&gt; - Fire-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ziost Guardian&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Old Forgotten Lightsaber&lt;/b&gt; - Electric Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Elegant Lightsaber&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Blue Shot Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Crossguard Knight&lt;/b&gt; - Ice-Light Projectile.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;All weapons have additional perks, (too many to list here) try them and see which they have!&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;This contains a custom SLink2 file.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you use another mod which edits the sound files, then this mod needs to be placed &lt;u&gt;higher&lt;/u&gt; in your TKMM mod list to ensure that they sound correctly.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;NOTE&lt;/b&gt;: Adding lots of weapons may cause game instability due to default heapsize, if you have any issues then I suggest also installing &lt;a class="Name" href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/515897"&gt;RSDB HeapSize Increase&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Since the look of the weapon itself is the primary reason for the mod, I have decided to NOT hide any part of it when fused. (Suggest "&lt;a class="Name" href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449762"&gt;Invisible Fuses&lt;/a&gt;" to maintain the look of the blade).&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;br&gt;TKMM required for installation &amp; only tested on TotK 1.2.1.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Included Changelog.txt has more info regarding the specifics of this mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/master_sabers_100_standalone_.zip" type="application/zip"/>
